{
  "message": "fix: handle relative tests/benches paths in --exclude-tests filter\n\nThe glob patterns */tests/* and */benches/* require a leading directory\ncomponent, so they fail to match paths like tests/foo.rs or benches/b.rs\noutput by ripgrep when using relative PROJECT_DIR. Added tests/* and\nbenches/* patterns to handle this case.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>",
